 representing the product inside.\n\nThe core question is: are you married to the current title? Because if you're open to changing it, that's the single biggest lever you have for improving hits and conversion. The story earns its own readers once they're in it. The problem is getting them to the door.", "embedding": [0.01247614435851574, 0.06908705085515976, -0.00962870940566063, -0.010547572746872902, 0.0819530040025711, 0.005141147878021002, 0.03072800301015377, -0.022959500551223755, -0.0013471415732055902, -0.05326787754893303, -0.03346254304051399, 0.051927514374256134, 0.02451932057738304, -0.01948665827512741, -0.04997348040342331, 0.011397669091820717, 0.034111734479665756, -0.028936952352523804, -0.026838334277272224, 0.02950587123632431, 0.02891976572573185, 0.040040355175733566, 0.10041122883558273, 0.00022359374270308763, 0.043098170310258865, -0.020275359973311424, -0.047004781663417816, 0.03151286393404007, -0.048377592116594315, -0.09331832081079483, 0.12579089403152466, 0.06084880977869034, 0.06124669685959816, -0.04308436065912247, 0.011071485467255116, -0.024730179458856583, -0.04254855588078499, 0.040908217430114746, 0.004729586187750101, -0.020795481279492378, 0.10086634010076523, -0.015535121783614159, -0.10633601993322372, 0.10949656367301941, -0.05920254811644554, -0.027402376756072044, 0.00808696635067463, -0.08623962104320526, -0.02859787456691265, 0.1031346395611763, -0.06010577082633972, 0.016173195093870163, 0.013202285394072533, -0.04951903596520424, -0.06494835019111633, 0.056763794273138046, -0.0037147204857319593, -0.03518681228160858, -0.002721326192840934, 0.007243071682751179, -0.012003191746771336, 0.0020876280032098293, 0.013605009764432907, 0.03027164936065674, 0.010466871783137321, -0.031770121306180954, 0.03155868500471115, 0.028223449364304543, -0.08974818140268326, 0.07814252376556396, 0.001411593984812498, 0.05012666806578636, 0.03725038841366768, 0.053763363510370255, 0.026191312819719315, 0.05763792246580124, -0.0257207